# Commit Changes in touchline_tantrum Repository

The goal is to commit the existing staged changes in the `touchline_tantrum` submodule. These changes primarily focus on removing Firebase dependencies in favor of mock services and local storage, introducing a new "Manager Mood" widget, and general code quality improvements.

## Proposed Changes

### touchline_tantrum Submodule

#### [MODIFY] [auth_service.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/services/auth_service.dart)
- Removed Firebase Auth and Google/Apple sign-in dependencies.
- Implemented a mock `AuthService` with a local `User` class for testing.

#### [MODIFY] [save_service.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/services/save_service.dart)
- Removed Firestore database integration.
- Switched to using `SharedPreferences` for local career persistence.

#### [NEW] [manager_mood.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/manager_mood.dart)
- Added a new widget that displays the manager's mood (happy, neutral, stressed, angry) based on team stats.

#### [MODIFY] [game_screen.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart)
- Updated logic to update manager mood based on performance and season goals.
- Added curly braces to control flow statements for code clarity.
- Minor UI layout and `const` optimizations.

#### [MODIFY] [breaking_news_ticker.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/breaking_news_ticker.dart), [settings_dialog.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/settings_dialog.dart), [stat_rings.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/stat_rings.dart), [trophy_cabinet.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/trophy_cabinet.dart), [career_select_screen.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/career_select_screen.dart)
- Applied general linting fixes (adding curly braces, `const` keywords, and property updates).

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `flutter analyze` inside the `touchline_tantrum` directory to ensure no new linting errors or breaks were introduced.
- Run existing unit tests if any (check for `test/` directory).

### Manual Verification
- Verify that the application builds correctly without Firebase dependencies.
- Check if the "Manager Mood" widget appears and updates correctly during gameplay.
